// TaskGraphView
// Renders the implementation task graph as a Mermaid diagram.
// Fetches the graph from the backend via useTaskGraph and passes the result
// to MermaidPreview with shared zoom controls from uiStore.

FUNCTION TaskGraphView(project, session) -> JSX                        EXPORT
  CALLS: MermaidPreview (MermaidPreview), useTaskGraph (useTaskGraph)
  Reads diagram, isLoading, error, refresh from useTaskGraph(project, session).
  Reads zoomLevel, zoomIn, zoomOut, setZoomLevel from uiStore.
  IF isLoading: shows centered spinner + "Loading task graph..." text.
  IF error: shows error card with message + Retry button (calls refresh).
  IF no diagram: shows empty state with icon and "Task graph will appear
  during implementation phase" message.
  ELSE: renders MermaidPreview with diagram content and zoom props.
